name: ProjectFactory
description: ProjectFactory. This contract is used by rigor to create cheap clones of Project contract underlying.

functionDecorators.name: createProject
functionDecorators.description: this function can only be called by Rigor contract. create a clone for project contract.

parameterDecorators.name: _currency
parameterDecorators.description: address of the currency used by project.

returnDecorators.name: _clone
returnDecorators.description: address of the clone project contract.

functionDecorators.name: initialize
functionDecorators.description: initialize this contract with rigor and master project address.

parameterDecorators.name: _underlying
parameterDecorators.description: the implementation address of project smart contract.

parameterDecorators.name: _homeFi
parameterDecorators.description: the latest address of rigor contract.
